summary: A beautiful woman is sent back in time via hypnosis to the Middle Ages where she finds she is suspected of being a witch, and subject to being executed.
cast: Pamela Duncan|Richard Garland|Allison Hayes|Val Dufour|Mel Welles|Dorothy Neumann|Billy Barty|Bruno VeSota|Richard Devon|Maurice Manson|Aaron Saxon|Don Garrett|Dick Miller|Paul Blaisdell|Signe Hack|Jack Tornek
title: La no muerta
